&lt;h1 id="the-unbundling-of-the-venture-capital-industry"&gt;The Unbundling of the Venture Capital Industry&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dec 1 2010&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;People often mock Super-Angels as being impure because they invest other people&amp;rsquo;s money. We also often get asked &amp;ldquo;What are VCs and Seed Funds doing on AngelList?&amp;rdquo; (They&amp;rsquo;re clearly marked, by the way, and you can choose who your pitch is visible to.)&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>How to Lose Time and Money</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/selfindulgence/</link><pubDate>Thu, 01 Jul 2010 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_en/selfindulgence/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;→ &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/paul_graham/essays_zh/selfindulgence/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
